object

password: string

name: string

Example

  "username": [

      "ordering-index": "integer",
      "secret": "string",
      "name": "string",

          {
            "name": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "password": "string",
      "password-policy": {
        "password": "string",
        "name": "string"
      }
    }
  ]
}

object

Destination host information

Peer Type

Enabled or disabled

Specify interface for source address in DIAMETER packets

VRF the peer belongs to

Timer value in seconds

Timer value in seconds
